 />\n黃錦良說，只有18間受訪學校有學生參與罷課，當中兩間小學，平均約10名學生參與。他認為，罷課學校數目少，教學普遍可有序開始，絕大部分老師都可謹守崗位。<br />\n<br />\n教聯會副主席王惠成建議，教育局就學校應付學生罷課提供更多指引，多與學校密切聯繫。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20190919/s00001/1568877681656/%e3%80%90%e9%80%83%e7%8a%af%e6%a2%9d%e4%be%8b%e3%80%91%e6%95%99%e8%81%af%e6%9c%83%e8%aa%bf%e6%9f%a5-%e5%9b%9b%e6%88%90%e5%ad%b8%e6%a0%a1%e7%a8%b1%e5%ad%b8%e7%94%9f%e7%8f%be%e6%83%85%e7%b7%92%e5%95%8f%e9%a1%8c-%e6%9c%89%e8%ad%a6%e5%af%9f%e5%ad%90%e5%a5%b3%e8%a2%ab%e6%8e%92%e6%93%a0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20190919%2Fs00001%2F1568877681656%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e9%2580%2583%25e7%258a%25af%25e6%25a2%259d%25e4%25be%258b%25e3%2580%2591%25e6%2595%2599%25e8%2581%25af%25e6%259c%2583%25e8%25aa%25bf%25e6%259f%25a5-%25e5%259b%259b%25e6%2588%2590%25e5%25ad%25b8%25e6%25a0%25a1%25e7%25a8%25b1%25e5%25ad%25b8%25e7%2594%259f%25e7%258f%25be%25e6%2583%2585%25e7%25b7%2592%25e5%2595%258f%25e9%25a1%258c-%25e6%259c%2589%25e8%25ad%25a6%25e5%25af%259f%25e5%25ad%2590%25e5%25a5%25b3%25e8%25a2%25ab%25e6%258e%2592%25e6%2593%25a0&d=gqDWnnaI%2FM4dwC7GJUFj5YlFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=7baacf09\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20190919%2Fs00001%2F1568877681656%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e9%2580%2583%25e7%258a%25af%25e6%25a2%259d%25e4%25be%258b%25e3%2580%2591%25e6%2595%2599%25e8%2581%25af%25e6%259c%2583%25e8%25aa%25bf%25e6%259f%25a5-%25e5%259b%259b%25e6%2588%2590%25e5%25ad%25b8%25e6%25a0%25a1%25e7%25a8%25b1%25e5%25ad%25b8%25e7%2594%259f%25e7%258f%25be%25e6%2583%2585%25e7%25b7%2592%25e5%2595%258f%25e9%25a1%258c-%25e6%259c%2589%25e8%25ad%25a6%25e5%25af%259f%25e5%25ad%2590%25e5%25a5%25b3%25e8%25a2%25ab%25e6%258e%2592%25e6%2593%25a0&h=9793d07b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20190919/s00001/1568877681656/%e3%80%90%e9%80%